title: Pre-wired for high speed internet, Private patios and balconies
posting_body: ['The Pulse Of Silicon Valley.', 'Plug Into Modern Living.', 'If you are searching for a place to live in the heart of Silicon Valley that reflects its innovative spirit and modern lifestyle, look no further than Avana Almaden.', 'We have tapped into this exciting and cutting-edge community to deliver modern apartment homes that perfectly accentuate the character of the city.', 'At Avana Almaden, an array of amenities provides a cozy and convenient place to stay plugged in when you are not spending time in the office.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 75', 'OR Text', '75', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text us.', 'Want more info on this unit?', 'See the link (below):', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 932 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Pre', '-wired for high speed internet', '- Convenient in-home washer and dryer', '- Additional storage available', '- New designer lighting and fixtures*', '- Private patios and balconies', '- Upgraded kitchens with stainless steel appliances and sleek quartz countertops*', '- Abundant closet space', 'Community Amenities', '- Cabana lounges and cozy fire pit', '- Picnic area', "- Bark Park and Bark n' Bubbles Dog Spa coming soon!", '- Relaxing hydro jet spa', '- Two swimming pools', '- Backyard barbecue grills', '- Covered parking available', '- Zen like scenery and tree lined walkways', '- Professionally managed', 'Pet Policy', 'We welcome cats and dogs.', 'Please call the Leasing Office for more details.', 'Income Requirements:', '3 times the rent', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Avana Almaden', '1070 Foxchase Dr, San Jose, CA, 95123', 'uAJTMPrp32e']
